  "title": "红杉美国等机构 4800 万美金超大额押注，四位学者做了一个细分领域的 AI coding 产品",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3NDc2MjQxMg==&mid=2247488420&idx=1&sn=af64593434711b04cf5c96a384ee9231",
  "date": "2025-07-03 00:35:00",
